    "Using Telugu dictionaries, a noun morphological stemmer and noun suffixes in which the first part discussed the identification of nouns.",
    "Using transliterated gazetteer listings associated to various context features, Named Entity tags, morphological characteristics, NE suffix features and the NEs are identified in the second part.",
    "Alfred et al. [55] proposed Malay articles using Rule-based entity recognition system.",
    "The context-specific features and Malay POS tagging capabilities that have been built to handle Malay articles are the foundation of the proposed Malay NER.",
    "Proper names will be recognized or found based on the POS findings as potential candidates for annotation."
